			<h2>What's in a <span class="green">Project</span> anyway?</h2>
			<p>	This tool allows you to create new projects which your requirements can be associated to. 
			Requirements can be further categorised using <strong>Groupings</strong>. A project should cover the development 
			or enhancement of a single solution while a Grouping will be limited to a functional area.<br /><br />
