			<h2>Activity <span class="green">Statistics</span></h2>
			<p>	When you move away from lengthy requirements documents initially it can seem harder to tell how your project 
			is really progressing. In an iterative development framework such as this one the best ways to establish the 
			health of your project is in the use of statistics which detail the level of activity.</p>
			<div class="rs">
			<ul>
				<li>New Requirements</li>
				<li>Updates/Changes</li>
				<li>Testing
